sources.title: Fangs of the Wild
sources.description: Foxes are mysteriously disappearing from fox farms and Agent Don (Dennis Moore) has been sent to investigate. Brad (George Chesebro) and Pete (Jimmy Aubrey) are the culprits and they are using a dog that can climb the security fence to steal the foxes. Don brings a dog with him and when Carol (Luana Walters) sees a dog stealing a fox, she accuses Don.

sources.title: Fangs of the Wild (1939) RIN TIN TIN
sources.description:
Stars: Dennis Moore, Luana Walters, Tom London
Director: Raymond K. Johnson

Foxes are mysteriously disappearing from fox farms and Agent Don has been sent to investigate. He discovers culprits are using a dog that can climb the security fence to steal the foxes!
